citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process from 11:50 AM to
12:20 PM on June 22, 2021.
The inspector tried to contact the licensee by knocking on the door, calling the licensees cell phone, and calling the
licensees wife's cell phone.
End Section
